metadata.name: Right-Click Save As Girl
metadata.description:
DIGITAL RENAISSPAM

The rapid transformation and evolution of digital technologies have given rise to a new generation of digital artists who are pushing the boundaries of art through the use of digital tools and techniques. These are digital artworks that are created using artificial intelligence, a democratizing force, enabling more artists to reach a wider audience and creating new opportunities for collaboration and experimentation. 

"Right-Click Save As Girl" is a Digital Renaisspam CC0 AI Art contain work of XCOPY, ROBNESS, Stellabelle, Max Capacity, The Perfesser, Loot, VLDZ and Bl33k.
